                                                                                                               Tata Tea taste for cold drinks
          A STAFF REPORTER                                            
	Calcutta, March 20: Tata Tea has entered the branded soft drink market with its cold beverage T!ON.        
	The drink will be available in three flavours  Mango Rush, Peach Punch and Apple Buzz. A 400-ml bottle will cost Rs 22.        
	The cold drink market in India is worth about Rs 1,000 crore.        
	The company said the move was part of a strategy to shift its focus to beverages. This is a defining moment in the history of Tata Tea as it symbolises the change taking place in the company, Tata Tea executive director Sangeeta Talwar said.        
	With this launch, we believe the beverage market in India will get a new momentum and provide exciting options to young India, she added.        
	Tata Tea has a presence in over 40 countries.                                                                                                                                       
